The paper deals with analyzing large-scale news data, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques (cs.CL, cs.IR). The study also involves analyzing the dynamics of media attention over time, which could fall under the category of social network analysis (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper deals with data analysis and visualization, which could fall under the categories of data mining (cs.SD) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
